doc.previous: IUCN members are states government agencies international nongovernmental organizations national nongovernmental organizations or other affiliates In 2014 IUCN had 1218 members The members can organize themselves in national or regional committees to promote cooperation In 2014 there were 56 national committees and 7 regional committees
